import React from "react";
import { Switcher, SwitcherItem, HeaderPanel, SwitcherDivider } from "@carbon/react";

const ProfilePanel = ({ isAccountPanelExpanded }) => {

        <SwitcherItem href="#" aria-label="Link ">
          Link
        </SwitcherItem>
        <SwitcherItem href="#" aria-label="Link ">
          Link
        </SwitcherItem>
        <SwitcherItem href="#" aria-label="Link ">
          Link
        </SwitcherItem>
        <SwitcherItem href="#" aria-label="Link ">
          Link
        </SwitcherItem>
        <SwitcherDivider />
        <SwitcherItem href="#" aria-label="Link ">
          Link
        </SwitcherItem>
      </Switcher>
    </HeaderPanel>
  );
};

export default ProfilePanel;
